Simple example inspired from LOH1 spice benchmark (http://www.sismowine.org/model/WP2_LOH1.pdf)

Configuration for 4 GPUs

edit (set path to specfem directory) and run

run_preproc.sh (on CPU) : for mesh and input file creation
run_specfem.sh (on GPU): simulation 

Check_result.py : python script to check the solution with respect to reference solution computed by specfem on 4 GPUs  NVIDIA RTX 6000 Ada


Runtime on 4 GPUs  NVIDIA RTX 6000 Ada : 
run_preproc.sh : ~4 mins
run_specfem.sh : ~5 mins 
 

